INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (33, N'58bd5b49-6552-4f6a-935d-c3007d8626c1', 17, 1, N'<p>CBeebies is dedicated to delighting and surprising its pre-school audience and it remains the UK&#39;s most watched and most loved channel for the under-sixes. CBBC, the sister channel, is for children aged 6-12.</p>

<p>To complement our commissioned programming the Children’s Acquisitions and Independent Animation team acquires and pre-buys material for CBeebies (children aged 0 - 6) and CBBC (children aged 6-12) from production companies in the UK and internationally.</p>

<p>We have a slightly different buying approach for each channel but deals are completed via a straightforward license agreement.</p>

<h2>0-6 year-olds</h2>

<p>For CBeebies our budget is utilised to buy animated series. We welcome ideas which demonstrate new ways to educate, inform, entertain and inspire a child’s first steps towards big ideas. Successful animations which reflect these ideas include What’s the Big Idea? (a pre-school philosophy show) Octonauts (an action-adventure show based around teamwork and marine biology) and Messy Goes to OKIDO (introducing complex scientific ideas to a very young audience).</p>

<p>In a crowded marketplace a highly distinctive visual is important alongside fresh, inventive and compelling characters. Ideas should be driven by an understanding of our audience and where possible inspire a sense of awe and wonder.</p>

<p><strong>Note:</strong> we do not acquire live-action programming and we rarely buy off the shelf animation for CBeebies. The most common way for CBeebies to acquire animation is through the pre-buy model as this ensures that all programmes are tailored to perfectly suit our very youngest viewers. This means we can make sure our programming is tonally right.</p>

<h2>6-16 year-olds</h2>

<p>We’re on the lookout for fresh and exciting ideas for animation and live action drama series with superb story-telling at the heart of the concept. For older viewers we like to see more complex stories with authentic characters and big rites of passage stories told sensitively.</p>

<p>Mustangs FC, The Next Step, Arthur, Odd Squad, Dennis and Gnasher Unleashed!, Scream Street, The Deep, Dragons Race to the Edge and Shaun the Sheep, are examples of programmes that have come through our department.</p>

<p>We are open to both pre-buys and completed programmes for CBBC.</p>

<ul>
	<li>We are currently on the lookout for a genre-busting adventure series that reaches beyond our current offering.</li>
	<li>We are also looking for a slightly older-skewing animated series, possibly a sitcom with sarky offbeat humour.</li>
	<li>We are still on the lookout for more content with strong, aspirational female characters.</li>
</ul>

<p></p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (34, N'4c5979ca-4be3-4de0-a0fb-b055a5221060', 17, 2, N'<p>O CBeebies dedica-se a encantar e surpreender o p&uacute;blico pr&eacute;-escolar e continua sendo o canal mais assistido e mais apreciado pelo Reino Unido para os menores de seis anos. O CBBC, o canal irm&atilde;o, &eacute; para crian&ccedil;as de 6 a 12 anos. Para complementar nossa programa&ccedil;&atilde;o encomendada, a equipe de Aquisi&ccedil;&otilde;es Infantis e Anima&ccedil;&atilde;o Independente adquire e pr&eacute;-compra material para CBeebies (crian&ccedil;as de 0 a 6 anos) e CBBC (crian&ccedil;as de 6 a 12 anos) de empresas de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o no Reino Unido e internacionalmente. Temos uma abordagem de compra ligeiramente diferente para cada canal, mas as transa&ccedil;&otilde;es s&atilde;o conclu&iacute;das por meio de um contrato de licen&ccedil;a simples. 0-6 anos de idade Para o CBeebies, nosso or&ccedil;amento &eacute; utilizado para comprar s&eacute;ries animadas. Congratulamo-nos com id&eacute;ias que demonstram novas maneiras de educar, informar, entreter e inspirar os primeiros passos de uma crian&ccedil;a para grandes id&eacute;ias. Anima&ccedil;&otilde;es bem-sucedidas que refletem essas ideias incluem Qual &eacute; a grande ideia? (um show de filosofia pr&eacute;-escola) Octonauts (um show de a&ccedil;&atilde;o e aventura baseado em trabalho de equipe e biologia marinha) e Messy Goes to OKIDO (apresentando id&eacute;ias cient&iacute;ficas complexas para um p&uacute;blico muito jovem). Em um mercado lotado, um visual altamente distinto &eacute; importante, juntamente com personagens novos, inventivos e atraentes. As ideias devem ser orientadas por uma compreens&atilde;o do nosso p&uacute;blico e, sempre que poss&iacute;vel, inspirar um sentimento de admira&ccedil;&atilde;o e admira&ccedil;&atilde;o. Nota: n&oacute;s n&atilde;o adquirimos a programa&ccedil;&atilde;o live-action e raramente compramos a anima&ccedil;&atilde;o da prateleira para o CBeebies. A maneira mais comum para o CBeebies adquirir anima&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; atrav&eacute;s do modelo de pr&eacute;-compra, pois isso garante que todos os programas sejam adaptados para se adequarem perfeitamente aos nossos espectadores mais jovens. Isso significa que podemos garantir que nossa programa&ccedil;&atilde;o esteja correta. 6-16 anos de idade Estamos &agrave; procura de ideias novas e excitantes para s&eacute;ries de anima&ccedil;&atilde;o e a&ccedil;&atilde;o ao vivo, com uma excelente narra&ccedil;&atilde;o de hist&oacute;rias no centro do conceito. Para os espectadores mais velhos, gostamos de ver hist&oacute;rias mais complexas com personagens aut&ecirc;nticos e grandes ritos de hist&oacute;rias de passagem contadas com sensibilidade. Mustangs FC, The Next Step, Arthur, Odd Squad, Dennis e Gnasher Unleashed !, Scream Street, The Deep, Dragons Race to the Edge e Shaun the Sheep, s&atilde;o exemplos de programas que vieram atrav&eacute;s do nosso departamento. Estamos abertos a programas pr&eacute;-compra e conclu&iacute;dos para o CBBC. Atualmente, estamos &agrave; procura de uma s&eacute;rie de aventuras de g&ecirc;nero que vai al&eacute;m de nossa atual oferta. Tamb&eacute;m estamos &agrave; procura de uma s&eacute;rie animada de inclina&ccedil;&atilde;o ligeiramente mais antiga, possivelmente uma com&eacute;dia de humor exc&ecirc;ntrico e sarc&aacute;stico. Ainda estamos &agrave; procura de mais conte&uacute;do com personagens femininos fortes e aspiracionais.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
