INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (75, N'ec099aa1-0156-418d-871c-8f45c99fdcd9', 38, 1, N'<p><strong>CHATRONE is a Los Angeles based production company founded by a Brazilian, Carina Schulze and an American, Aaron Berger. In 2012, they created CHATRONE LATIN AMERICA in Brazil with offices in Rio de Janeiro and S&atilde;o Paulo.</strong></p>

<p></p>

<p><strong>Chatrone’s first Brazilian production was the smash hit, GABY ESTRELLA, a co-production with Panoramica. Carina is the creator and showrunner for this series, a musical for kids and teens. The series had three seasons (124 episodes) aired on Gloob. GABY has doubled the channel’s ratings and has a series of licensed products in the market, such as notebooks, backpacks, and an original soundtrack.</strong></p>

<p><strong>GABY ESTRELLA has won the Monet Magazine Award for Best Teen Series, beating international hits like “Pretty Little Liars,” “The Carrie Diaries,” and “Violetta.” GABY was nominated for a 2015 INTERNATIONAL EMMY AWARD- the most prestigious international award for a TV show - for Best Kids Series and for the ROCKIE AWARDS of BANFF FESTIVAL (Canada) as “Kids TV Show”, for it’s second season.</strong></p>

<p><strong>In 2014, THE BOOK OF LIFE, an animated feature produced by Aaron and Carina and distributed by FOX, had a worldwide premiere. The movie was nominated at the Golden Globes for Best Animated Feature and won an Annie Award for Best Character Design, among other nominations. It has made over 95 million dollars in cinemas around the globe. </strong></p>

<p><strong>Chatrone, in a coproduction with Panoramica, produced the action series SEM VOLTA (NO RETURN), for adults. The series aired on Record TV in 2017. </strong></p>

<p><strong>The company produced the tween surf series, JUACAS, created and developed by Carina Schulze – who was also the showrunner of the show. The series has 26 episodes, was a co-production with Cinefilm and aired in 2017 on Disney XD Latin America.</strong></p>

<p><strong>In January 2018, CHATRONE will release GABY ESTRELLA, a feature film for the whole family, based on the series GABY ESTRELLA. It’s a musical drama and the script was written by Carina.</strong></p>

<p><strong>The company is currently developing projects for the international market, as an animated series for Amazon US and two series for Discovery Latin America.</strong></p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (76, N'f2f3c926-d198-43de-b957-dba0a24f20c1', 38, 2, N'<p><strong>Chatrone &eacute; uma produtora fundada pela brasileira Carina Schulze e o americano Aaron Berger. H&aacute; cinco anos, eles montaram a Chatrone Latin America no Brasil.</strong></p>

<p></p>

<p><strong>Em 2014, Aaron e Carina produziram o longa americano de anima&ccedil;&atilde;o Festa no C&eacute;u (The Book Of Life) em parceria com Guillermo Del Toro, distribu&iacute;do pela FOX USA. O filme foi indicado ao Globo de Ouro de melhor anima&ccedil;&atilde;o, ao Critics Choice Awards de melhor anima&ccedil;&atilde;o, Producers Guild of America de melhor produ&ccedil;&atilde;o em longa de anima&ccedil;&atilde;o e ganhou um Annie na categoria de melhor design de personagem, al&eacute;m de arrecadar milh&otilde;es de d&oacute;lares em bilheterias do mundo inteiro.</strong></p>

<p><strong>A primeira produ&ccedil;&atilde;o da Chatrone no Brasil foi Gaby Estrella. A s&eacute;rie musical infantil teve tr&ecirc;s temporadas, um longa-metragem que ser&aacute; lan&ccedil;ado em 2018 e ainda tem diversos produtos licenciados, como mochilas, cadernos, &aacute;lbum de figurinha e CD com a trilha sonora original.</strong></p>

<p><strong>Gaby ganhou o Pr&ecirc;mio Monet de Melhor S&eacute;rie Teen de Televis&atilde;o e foi indicada a dois pr&ecirc;mios internacionais: Emmy International 2015, o principal pr&ecirc;mio de televis&atilde;o, e ao Rockie Awards, do Banff Festival no Canad&aacute;.</strong></p>

<p><strong>Ainda no Brasil, em 2017 foi ao ar a s&eacute;rie de a&ccedil;&atilde;o Sem Volta, na Record, outra coprodu&ccedil;&atilde;o com a Panor&acirc;mica.</strong></p>

<p><strong>Em 2017, Chatrone lan&ccedil;ou a s&eacute;rie de a&ccedil;&atilde;o Sem Volta, na Record, outra co-produ&ccedil;&atilde;o com a Panor&acirc;mica. E tamb&eacute;m lan&ccedil;ou Juacas, no Disney Channel. Juacas &eacute; uma s&eacute;rie de a&ccedil;&atilde;o e aventura sobre surf para o p&uacute;blico infanto-juvenil e &eacute; uma co-produ&ccedil;&atilde;o entre Chatrone e Cinefilm. A s&eacute;rie estreou simultaneamente no Brasil, em toda Am&eacute;rica Latina e na It&aacute;lia. Juacas ficou em primeiro lugar na It&aacute;lia. </strong></p>

<p><strong>Atualmente, a empresa se dedica ao desenvolvimento de projetos para o mercado internacional, dentre eles, uma s&eacute;rie de anima&ccedil;&atilde;o para a Amazon US e duas s&eacute;ries infantis para a Discovery Latin America.</strong></p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (77, N'997064c5-fac8-48ca-8535-a475de81d681', 39, 1, N'<p>CINEBRASiLTV brings to the public a refined cinematographic language. The author&#39;s view, aware of the power of the image, who leads the critical viewer to reflect on the Brazilian cultural transformations. Our programming communicates the current situation in Brazil to those who have a thirst for knowledge, empowerment and identity. Our content has a soul, inspires the desire to know, discusses the truths of history and the sense of justice with a contemporary view. Investigative documentaries, which bring to the viewer what the mainstream media has avoided doing. Unpublished fictional series that reflect behaviors, conflicts and human relations. Documentary series that rescue traditions from the deep Brazil. At CINEBRASiLTV, the simplicity and authenticity of ordinary people has style: a warmer, conscious, poetic and pop universe. Another world is possible.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (78, N'fe83647a-8ce0-46ea-b5c3-c20fd87decd8', 39, 2, N'<p>O CINEBRASiLTV traz ao grande p&uacute;blico uma linguagem cinematogr&aacute;fica refinada. Aqui &eacute; o olhar do autor, ciente da for&ccedil;a de comunica&ccedil;&atilde;o da imagem, quem conduz o espectador cr&iacute;tico a refletir sobre as transforma&ccedil;&otilde;es culturais brasileiras.<br />
<br />
Exclusiva e original, nossa programa&ccedil;&atilde;o comunica a atualidade do Brasil para quem tem sede de conhecimento, de empoderamento e de identidade. <br />
<br />
O nosso conte&uacute;do tem alma, inspira o desejo de saber, fala das verdades da Hist&oacute;ria e do sentido de justi&ccedil;a com um olhar contempor&acirc;neo para o futuro. A for&ccedil;a da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o em sua complexa engenharia de realidade.<br />
<br />
Document&aacute;rios autorais investigativos, que trazem ao espectador o que a grande m&iacute;dia se furtou a fazer. S&eacute;ries ficcionais in&eacute;ditas que refletem comportamentos, conflitos e rela&ccedil;&otilde;es humanas. S&eacute;ries documentais que resgatam tradi&ccedil;&otilde;es das curvas do Brasil profundo. <br />
<br />
No CINEBRASiLTV a simplicidade e a autenticidade de gente comum tem estilo: um universo mais quente e humano, consciente e forte, po&eacute;tico e pop. Um outro mundo &eacute;  poss&iacute;vel. E ele &eacute; mais do seu jeito.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (79, N'20d183c6-a467-45b9-9485-17b0698c11a3', 40, 1, N'<p>CISUP - Companhia de Imagens e Sons is an independent audiovisual producer and manager of cultural projects, founded in 2000, based in Belo Horizonte, Minas Gerais, Brazil. Specializing in the production of audiovisual content, consulting on the creation of formats and multiplatform content management. Associated with BRAVI (Brasil Audiovisual) since 2005, registered in ANCINE (Ag&ecirc;ncia Nacional de Cinema), it stands out in the regional TV production in Brazil with more than 4,000 hours of production of its own content and coproduced, mainly for TV open. We also produce more than a hundred advertising pieces for the market.<br />
The "Via&ccedil;&atilde;o Cip&oacute;" (824 X 46 &#39;HD), a journal of journalistic varieties with themes of tourism, culture, cuisine, environment, handicrafts and music, has been featured in the air since 2003 by TV Alterosa / SBT of Minas Gerais, to 830 (eight hundred and thirty municipalities) of the state, in two editions for an estimated audience of over twenty million viewers.<br />
CISUP LTDA ME has a repertoire of new formats in the pre-production phase and some already with ready-made drivers such as the "KD1-KD1", "Horse Enchanting" and "Easy to Eat Well!" Programs. We highlight the co-production with South Africa of the series of 13 (thirteen) episodes of "Express Caipirinha". Check out the teaser: https://vimeo.com/138363312<br />
We participate in various international events such as congresses, workshops, and fairs. Highlights include the participation as an exhibitor at the Sine Side of the Doc in La Rochelle / FR in 2008 and eight editions of "MIPCOM" (largest event, Congress and TV content fair in the world) in Cannes / FR from 2009 to 2015. The documentary "Duas Torres de Sant&egrave;", among other coproduction projects such as the "Pequeninos" animation, still under development, is in pre-production.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (80, N'8be15f84-12db-48b0-8110-1b9b60a02419', 40, 2, N'<p><strong>A CISUP - Companhia de Imagens e Sons &eacute; uma produtora de audiovisuais independente e gestora de projetos culturais, fundada em 2000, sediada em Belo Horizonte, Minas Gerais, Brasil. Especializada em produzir conte&uacute;do audiovisual, prestar consultoria na cria&ccedil;&atilde;o de formatos e gest&atilde;o de conte&uacute;dos multiplataforma. Associada a BRAVI (Brasil Audiovisual) desde 2005, registrada na ANCINE (Ag&ecirc;ncia Nacional de Cinema), se destaca na produ&ccedil;&atilde;o regional de TV no Brasil com mais de 4.000 (Quatro mil) horas de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o de conte&uacute;do pr&oacute;prio e coproduzido exibido, sobretudo para TV aberta. Produzimos tamb&eacute;m mais de uma centena de pe&ccedil;as publicit&aacute;rias para o mercado.</strong></p>

<p><strong>Com destaque na consagrada coprodu&ccedil;&atilde;o semanal a “Via&ccedil;&atilde;o Cip&oacute;” (824 X 46’ HD), uma revista de variedades jornal&iacute;sticas com temas do turismo, cultura, culin&aacute;ria, meio-ambiente, artesanato e m&uacute;sica, no ar desde 2003 pela TV Alterosa / SBT de Minas, exibido para 830 (oitocentos e trinta munic&iacute;pios) do estado, em duas edi&ccedil;&otilde;es para um p&uacute;blico estimado em mais de vinte milh&otilde;es de telespectadores.</strong></p>

<p><strong>A CISUP LTDA ME conta com um repert&oacute;rio de novos formatos em fase de pr&eacute;- produ&ccedil;&atilde;o e alguns j&aacute; com pilotos prontos, como os programas “KD1-KD1”, “Encantador de Cavalos” e “&Eacute; f&aacute;cil comer bem!”. Destacamos a coprodu&ccedil;&atilde;o com a &Aacute;frica do Sul a s&eacute;rie de 13 (treze) epis&oacute;dios do “Express Caipirinha”. Confiram o teaser: https://vimeo.com/138363312</strong></p>

<p><strong>Participamos de v&aacute;rios eventos internacionais como congressos, workshops e feiras. Em destaque a participa&ccedil;&atilde;o como exibidora no “Sine Side Of the Doc” em La Rochelle/FR em 2008 e de oito edi&ccedil;&otilde;es do “MIPCOM” (maior evento, congresso e feira de conte&uacute;do para TV do mundo) em Cannes/FR de 2009 a 2015. Est&aacute; em pr&eacute;-produ&ccedil;&atilde;o o document&aacute;rio: “Duas Torres de Sant&egrave;”, dentre outros projetos de coprodu&ccedil;&atilde;o como a anima&ccedil;&atilde;o “Pequeninos” ainda em fase de desenvolvimento.</strong></p>
