INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (391, N'b7f0e452-0e26-458b-a3f9-ac659bd4a255', 196, 1, N'<p>TV UNAM is the cultural channel of the National Autonomous University of Mexico. The biggest and most important university of Latin America</p>

<p>In the last 8 years TVUNAM has become a benchmark in the Mexican cultural tv scene. It can be seen throughout all the Mexican territory via pay tv, and over 26 major cities via DTT. With the help of different institutions, TVUNAM’s satellite signal covers the whole country, reaching over 600 cities, and thanks to an agreement signed with the SPR, we can be seen in 26 major cities through Digital Terrestrial Television. All this platforms allows us to reach 56% of the potential national audiences.</p>

<p>Our programming grid gathers domestic productions of a wide range of themes with the best quality standars, contents obtained through different institutions and some samples of the best cultural programs of all the World. TV UNAM thereby created a unique style through productions and tv broadcasts that show the diversity, the cultural, artistic, scientific and knowledge heritage of our University. Driving the development of new languages ??and media formats.  </p>

<p>Throughout its career, the University network has been recognized with over 200 awards and distinctions, among which are: the award for Best Cultural Channel in Latin America by the Carlos III University of Madrid, three-time National Journalism Award granted by the People’s Council, among this highlights the prize obtained by the series The Mexican People in 2012 and, thanks to its participation as co-producer with BreakThru Films of Great Britain and Se-Ma-For Studios of Poland, shared the renowned Oscar for Best Animated Short Film in 2008.</p>

<p>As part of their projection in new technology platforms, in addition to their regular webcasts, TV UNAM also can be viewed in any device such as mobile phones or tablets, and it’s presence on social networks is growing constantly, both in social media, as well as it&#39;s web platform.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (392, N'4a757775-3929-4086-83ca-2e381a9e272d', 196, 2, N'<p>TV UNAM &eacute; o canal cultural da Universidade Nacional Aut&ocirc;noma do M&eacute;xico. A maior e mais importante universidade da Am&eacute;rica Latina<br />
Nos &uacute;ltimos 8 anos, a TVUNAM se tornou refer&ecirc;ncia no cen&aacute;rio cultural da televis&atilde;o mexicana. Pode ser visto em todo o territ&oacute;rio mexicano via pay tv, e mais de 26 grandes cidades via TDT. Com a ajuda de diferentes institui&ccedil;&otilde;es, o sinal de sat&eacute;lite da TVUNAM cobre todo o pa&iacute;s, alcan&ccedil;ando mais de 600 cidades, e gra&ccedil;as a um acordo assinado com a SPR, podemos ser vistos em 26 grandes cidades atrav&eacute;s da Televis&atilde;o Digital Terrestre. Todas essas plataformas nos permitem atingir 56% das audi&ecirc;ncias nacionais em potencial.<br />
Nossa grade de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o re&uacute;ne produ&ccedil;&otilde;es nacionais de uma ampla gama de temas com os melhores padr&otilde;es de qualidade, conte&uacute;dos obtidos atrav&eacute;s de diferentes institui&ccedil;&otilde;es e algumas amostras dos melhores programas culturais de todo o mundo. A TV UNAM criou assim um estilo &uacute;nico atrav&eacute;s de produ&ccedil;&otilde;es e transmiss&otilde;es televisivas que mostram a diversidade, o patrim&oacute;nio cultural, art&iacute;stico, cient&iacute;fico e de conhecimento da nossa Universidade. Impulsionando o desenvolvimento de novas linguagens e formatos de m&iacute;dia.<br />
Ao longo de sua carreira, a rede universit&aacute;ria foi reconhecida com mais de 200 pr&ecirc;mios e distin&ccedil;&otilde;es, entre os quais: o pr&ecirc;mio de Melhor Canal Cultural da Am&eacute;rica Latina pela Universidade Carlos III de Madri, tr&ecirc;s vezes Pr&ecirc;mio Nacional de Jornalismo concedido pelo Conselho do Povo, entre estes destaca o pr&ecirc;mio obtido pela s&eacute;rie The Mexican People em 2012 e, gra&ccedil;as &agrave; sua participa&ccedil;&atilde;o como co-produtor com BreakThru Films da Gr&atilde;-Bretanha e Se-Ma-For Studios da Pol&ocirc;nia, compartilhou o renomado Oscar de Melhor Curta-Metragem de Anima&ccedil;&atilde;o em 2008.<br />
Como parte de sua proje&ccedil;&atilde;o em novas plataformas tecnol&oacute;gicas, al&eacute;m de seus webcasts regulares, a TV UNAM tamb&eacute;m pode ser visualizada em qualquer dispositivo, como celulares ou tablets, e sua presen&ccedil;a nas redes sociais est&aacute; crescendo constantemente, tanto nas m&iacute;dias sociais, quanto nas redes sociais. como &eacute; a plataforma web.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[OrganizationDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [OrganizationId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (393, N'8764ef16-e875-4900-836c-9b939401d509', 197, 1, N'<p>UOL is the largest Brazilian online content and digital services company, since its launch in April 1996.According to Omniture, UOL audience covers more than 80% of the Brazilian internet audience. Its content properties reaches more than 7.5 billion monthly page views; and its home page reaches more than 60 million of unique visitors every month. UOL is a pioneer company in the Brazilian internet environment and has been playing a key role in the Brazilians’ digital inclusion. The company offers the most extensive Portuguese online content, with more than 1,000 channels on journalism, information and entertainment. In addition to the news content, UOL also offers the most complete platform of products and services for the Brazilian internet users, including:online music streaming, security solutions (anti virus, firewall), online education, hosting services (domain registration, webhosting and website builder, webstore platform, etc), cloud computing platform and complete solution for online and mobile payments, among others. Throughout its 20 years, UOL has become a reference in technology and innovation as it keeps pace with technological advancement and internet users providing complete and integrated solutions.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
