<p>Our vast catalog features more than a century of music and comprises the largest, most diverse and multi-cultural music collection ever.</p>

<p>With the advancement of digital technology and the ever-changing world, our unparalleled commitment is to lead the development of new services, platforms and business models for delivery of music and related content, enabling innovations and enabling new business and artistic opportunities for flourish</p>

<p>Knowing that music is a powerful force for good in the world, it is unique in its ability to inspire people and bring them closer together, we work with our artists and staff to serve our communities.</p>

<p>We are home to the greatest artists, innovative and enterprising people of music.</p>

<p>Together, we are UMG, the Universal Music Group.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.463' AS DateTime), 1)
