<p>Some of our feature films produced: 2009 Oscar nominee &ldquo;&Uacute;ltima Parada 174&rdquo; (Paramount), &ldquo;Ilha R&aacute;-Tim-Bum&rdquo; (Warner), &ldquo;Eliana em O Segredo dos Golfinhos&rdquo; (Fox), &ldquo;O Mist&eacute;rio da Estrada de Sintra&rdquo; (Brazil-Portugal co-production, &ldquo;Ros&aacute;rio Tijeras&rdquo; (Mexico-Colombia-France-Brazil co-production).</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
