INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (197, N'4d016eee-2f9b-4597-b51f-44ce24521749', 100, 1, N'<p>Pandora Filmes (Providence Films) is an arthouse distribution company active in Brasil since 1989. Focusing especially on auteur cinema, the company have always tried to broad the arthouse film distribution in Brazil, relaunching memorable classics of well-known directors like Fellini, Bergman and Billy Wilder, and also revealing new names, once unknown, like Wong Kar-Wai, Atom Egoyan and Agn&eacute;s Jaoui.</p>

<p>The first films released by Pandora were &ldquo;Little Vera&rdquo; by Vasili Pichul; &ldquo;Dark Habits&rdquo; by Pedro Almodovar; &ldquo;A short film about love&rdquo; by Krzysztof Kieslowski; &ldquo;Trainspotting&rdquo; by Danny Boyle; &ldquo;Chungking Express&rdquo; by Wong Kar-Wai; &ldquo;Sex and Lucia&rdquo; by Julio Medem. In addition, the first classics relaunches were &ldquo;The nights of Cabiria&rdquo; by Frederico Felinni and &ldquo;Some Like it Hot&rdquo; by Billy Wilder.</p>

<p>Due to the great receptivity of the public which guarantees the interest of exhibitors, Pandora Filmes was able to reassure its proposal as one of the most important gateways for films that once were very hard to gain access into the Brazilian market. Here are a few examples of these tittles: &ldquo;HAHAHA&rdquo; and &ldquo;In another country&rdquo; by the south-korean Hong Sang-soo; the awarded german &ldquo;Barbara&rdquo; by Christian Petzold; &ldquo;L&rsquo;ecume du jours&rdquo; by the french Michel Gondry; &ldquo;Skylab&rdquo; by the also french Julie Delpy; the uruguayan &ldquo;Mr. Kaplan&rdquo; by Alvaro Brechner; the croatian &ldquo;Priest children&rdquo; by Vinko Bresan; and the franco-german &ldquo;Diplomacy&rdquo; by Volker Schlondorff.</p>

<p>Among international releases, Pandora also keeps in its annual catalogue national releases, from important brazilian directors acclaimed by the critics such as: Gustavo Steimberg; Rodolfo Nanni, Rubens Rewald, S&eacute;rgio Bianchi, Anna Muylaert, among others. In this segment we can highlight the films: &ldquo;Dom&eacute;sticas&rdquo; by Fernando Meirelles e Nando Olival with more than 74.000 admissions; &ldquo;Invasor&rdquo; by Beto Brant with 104.000 admissions; &ldquo;O Tapete Vermelho&rdquo; by Luiz Alberto Pereira with 105.000 admissions and most importantly &ldquo;Que horas ela volta?&rdquo;(The second mother) by Anna Muylaert with more than 500.000 admissions, a true phenomenon of art house releases.</p>

<p>Recently, Pandora released the spanish &ldquo;Truman&rdquo; by Cesc Gay, with Ricardo Dar&iacute;n reaching almost 200.000 admissions and the 2017 Oscar winner &ldquo;The Salesman&rdquo; by Asghar Farhadi. For the beginning of 2018 the company will also release 2017 Palme d&rsquo;Or: the swedish &ldquo;The Square&rdquo;.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (198, N'd5425f3b-eb91-4235-ae34-18877cc0a1af', 100, 2, N'<p>A Pandora Filmes &eacute; uma distribuidora de filmes de arte, ativa no Brasil desde 1989. Voltada especialmente para o cinema de autor, a distribuidora buscou, desde sua origem, ampliar os horizontes da distribui&ccedil;&atilde;o de filmes de arte no Brasil com relan&ccedil;amentos de cl&aacute;ssicos memor&aacute;veis em c&oacute;pias restauradas, de diretores como Fellini, Bergman e Billy Wilder, e revela&ccedil;&otilde;es de nomes outrora desconhecidos no pa&iacute;s, como Wong Kar-Wai, Atom Egoyan e Agn&eacute;s Jaoui.</p>

<p>A safra inaugural da distribuidora foi formada por filmes como A Pequena Vera, de Derek Jarman; Maus H&aacute;bitos, de Pedro Almodovar; N&atilde;o Amar&aacute;s, de Krystof Kieslowski; Trainspotting, de Danny Boyle; Amores Expressos, de Wong Kar-Wai; Lucia e o Sexo, de Julio Medem; e os festejados relan&ccedil;amentos de cl&aacute;ssicos mundiais como Noites de Cab&iacute;ria, de Federico Fellini e Quanto Mais Quente Melhor, de Billy Wilder.</p>

<p>Gra&ccedil;as &agrave; &oacute;tima receptividade do p&uacute;blico, o que garante cada vez mais espa&ccedil;o no circuito exibidor, a proposta da Pandora Filmes se firma ao longo de todos esses anos como uma das principais portas de entrada para filmes que antes eram pouco acess&iacute;veis no mercado brasileiro, a exemplo de &ldquo;HAHAHA&rdquo; e &ldquo;A Visitante Francesa&rdquo;, ambos do sul-coreano Hong Sang-soo; o premiado alem&atilde;o &ldquo;Barbara&rdquo;, de Christian Petzold; &ldquo;A Espuma dos Dias&rdquo;, com dire&ccedil;&atilde;o do franc&ecirc;s Michel Gondry; &ldquo;O Ver&atilde;o de Skylab&rdquo;, da tamb&eacute;m francesa Julie Delpy; o uruguaio &ldquo;Sr. Kaplan&rdquo;, de &Aacute;lvaro Brechner; o croata &ldquo;Os Filhos do Padre&rdquo;, dirigido por Vinko Bre&scaron;an; e o franco-alem&atilde;o &ldquo;Diplomacia&rdquo;, de Volker Schl&ouml;ndorff.</p>

<p>Paralelamente aos filmes internacionais, a Pandora Filmes sempre mant&eacute;m em seu cat&aacute;logo anual o lan&ccedil;amento de importantes filmes brasileiros, sucessos de cr&iacute;tica, de diretores como Gustavo Steimberg, Rodolfo Nanni, Rubens Rewald, S&eacute;rgio Bianchi, Roberto Moreira, entre outros. Neste contexto, destacam-se os lan&ccedil;amentos de Dom&eacute;sticas, de Fernando Meirelles e Nando Olival, com 74 mil espectadores; O Invasor, de Beto Brant, com 104 mil espectadores; Noel, o poeta da vila, de Ricardo van Steen com 50 mil espectadores; e O tapete vermelho de Luiz Alberto Pereira com 105 mil espectadores.</p>

<p>Para centrar ainda mais for&ccedil;a no cinema nacional, em 2015, a produtora Paula Cosenza se associou &agrave; distribuidora. Dentro desse segmento, destaca-se o recente &ldquo;Que Horas Ela Volta&rdquo;, de Anna Muylaert, um grande sucesso nacional, visto no cinema por mais de 500 mil espectadores firmando a Pandora como uma das mais importantes distribuidoras de filmes de arte no Brasil.</p>

<p>Recentemente, a Pandora lan&ccedil;ou no Brasil o premiado filme espanhol &ldquo;Truman&rdquo;, de Cesc Gay, com Ricardo Dar&iacute;n, que obteve quase 200 mil espectadores nos cinemas; al&eacute;m de distribuir o Oscar de melhor filme estrangeiro de 2017, o iraniano &ldquo;O Apartamento&rdquo;, de Asghard Farhadi. No in&iacute;cio de 2018, a distribuidora lan&ccedil;ar&aacute; o longa vencedor da Palma de Ouro de Cannes 2017, o sueco &ldquo;The Square&rdquo;.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (199, N'3f4b9e21-b8ab-4655-9a9a-30e20f9b6cab', 101, 1, N'<p>PANOR&Acirc;MICA&nbsp;is an independent production company founded in 2003 and based in Rio de Janeiro and S&atilde;o Paulo. PANOR&Acirc;MICA creates and produces TV series in diverse genres such as fiction, international formats, reality shows and branded content for TV channels like Globo, Record, Universal Channel, MTV, A&amp;E, Gloob, among others. PANOR&Acirc;MICA has created and produced the successful kids live action show GABY ESTRELLA(126x 24&acute;), which has licensed numerous products, from CD to school and party kits. The show was nominated for the EMMY KIDS AWARDS and BANFF and sold to other territories. The theatrical movie of GABY ESTRELLA will be released in January/2018, in Brazil.&nbsp;</p>

<p>In 2017, PANOR&Acirc;MICA&nbsp; first primetime fiction series - NO RETURN (13x48min) - was exhibited at TV Record and A&amp;E. In March 2018, TRAILS OF HATE (10x48&acute;), a police drama for NBC/Universal will be released. In 2018 PANOR&Acirc;MICA will produce other 5 tv series, and 2 feature films for the main channels and distributors in Brazil.&nbsp;</p>

<p>Panoramica has also created and produced in 2013 and 2014 the Globosat Writing Development Program, which has trained more than 400 writers and professionals of the Brazilian TV industry. The project brought to Brazil important names of the American TV Series industry such as Martha Kauffman (Friends), Anthony Zuicker (CSI), Darren Starr (Sex and the City), Dan Halstead (Manage-ment), and the master of writing Robert Mckee with his world famous seminars STORY and GENRE.</p>

<p>In Brazil, PANOR&Acirc;MICA has been using different ways to finance its shows, such as incentive laws, national funds, branded content, festival pitchings and full commissioning, always finding the best way to turn their ideas into viable and high quality products.</p>

<p>Creating and producing strong Intellectual Properties is PANOR&Acirc;MICA main goal for the next&nbsp;years.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (200, N'53da8999-083e-4e4f-8242-f101a69c3a45', 101, 2, N'<p>A&nbsp;PANOR&Acirc;MICA&nbsp;&eacute; uma produtora independente, fundada em 2003 e com sedes no Rio de Janeiro e S&atilde;o Paulo.&nbsp;A PANOR&Acirc;MICA cria e produz s&eacute;ries de TV de diversos g&ecirc;neros, como fic&ccedil;&atilde;o, formatos internacionais, reality shows e&nbsp;branded content&nbsp;para canais de TV como Globo, Record, Universal Channel, MTV, A&amp;E e Gloob, entre outros. A PANOR&Acirc;MICA criou e produziu&nbsp;a famosa s&eacute;rie infantil&nbsp;GABY ESTRELLA&nbsp;com 3 temporadas &ndash;&nbsp;126&nbsp;epis&oacute;dios de&nbsp;24minutos,&nbsp;propriedade que gerou licenciamento de&nbsp;uma variedade de produtos&nbsp;como&nbsp;CDs, material escolar,&nbsp;kits de festa&nbsp;etc.&nbsp;A s&eacute;rie&nbsp;foi indicada&nbsp;para os pr&ecirc;mios EMMY KIDS e BANFF e vendida&nbsp;para&nbsp;diversos pa&iacute;ses. O&nbsp;longa de GABY ESTRELLA ser&aacute; lan&ccedil;ado em&nbsp;2018.&nbsp;</p>

<p>Em 2017, foi exibida a primeira s&eacute;rie da PANOR&Acirc;MICA em hor&aacute;rio nobre na TV Aberta - SEM VOLTA (13 X 48min), de a&ccedil;&atilde;o e aventura,&nbsp;foi exibida na TV Record e no A&amp;E. Em Mar&ccedil;o/2018 estrear&aacute; sua s&eacute;rie ROTAS DO &Oacute;DIO, um drama policial para a NBC/Universal Channel. Em 2018 a PANOR&Acirc;MICA produzir&aacute; outras 5 s&eacute;ries de tv e 2 longa metragem, para alguns dos mais importantes canais e distribuidores do mercado brasileiro.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

<p>Em 2013 e 2014, a Panor&acirc;mica tamb&eacute;m criou e produziu o Programa Globosat de Desenvolvimento de Roteiristas, que treinou mais de 400 roteiristas e profissionais da ind&uacute;stria&nbsp;audiovisual&nbsp;brasileira.&nbsp; O projeto trouxe ao pa&iacute;s importantes nomes da ind&uacute;stria de seriados&nbsp;da&nbsp;TV americana como Martha Kauffman (Friends), Anthony Zuicker (CSI), Darren Starr (Sex and the City), Dan Halstead (Gest&atilde;o), e o mestre de roteiros, Robert Mckee, com seus semin&aacute;rios famosos em todo o mundo: HIST&Oacute;RIA e G&Ecirc;NERO.</p>

<p>No Brasil, a Panor&acirc;mica&nbsp;trabalha com todos os modelos de financiamento,&nbsp;tais como leis de incentivo,&nbsp;Fundo Setorial do Audiovisual,&nbsp;Branded Content,&nbsp;entre outros, sempre encontrando a melhor forma de transformar ideias em produtos vi&aacute;veis e de qualidade.</p>

<p>O principal objetivo da PANOR&Acirc;MICA para os pr&oacute;ximos anos &eacute; criar e produzir propriedade intelectual de alta qualidade.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
