INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (283, N'0b98afbd-572e-48fb-96d4-c82a4a351f81', 143, 1, N'<p>UOL is the largest Brazilian online content and digital services company, since its launch in April 1996.According to Omniture, UOL audience covers more than 80% of the Brazilian internet audience. Its content properties reaches more than 7.5 billion monthly page views; and its home page reaches more than 60 million of unique visitors every month. UOL is a pioneer company in the Brazilian internet environment and has been playing a key role in the Brazilians&rsquo; digital inclusion. The company offers the most extensive Portuguese online content, with more than 1,000 channels on journalism, information and entertainment. In addition to the news content, UOL also offers the most complete platform of products and services for the Brazilian internet users, including:online music streaming, security solutions (anti virus, firewall), online education, hosting services (domain registration, webhosting and website builder, webstore platform, etc), cloud computing platform and complete solution for online and mobile payments, among others. Throughout its 20 years, UOL has become a reference in technology and innovation as it keeps pace with technological advancement and internet users providing complete and integrated solutions.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (284, N'1268b9e8-a866-48b8-bb30-06c7794471aa', 143, 2, N'<p>O UOL &eacute; a maior empresa brasileira de conte&uacute;do, servi&ccedil;os digitais e tecnologia. Com cobertura de 80% da internet brasileira (8 em cada 10 internautas acessam o UOL todos os meses) sua homepage recebe mais de 60 milh&otilde;es de visitantes &uacute;nicos/m&ecirc;s. Pioneiro na internet brasileira, em 2016 o UOL completa 20 anos de trajet&oacute;ria, oferecendo mais de 1.000 canais de jornalismo, informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, entretenimento e servi&ccedil;os. O UOL tamb&eacute;m oferece&nbsp;aplicativos, todos gratuitos, para celulares e tablets, como Placar UOL, UOL Cota&ccedil;&otilde;es, UOL Not&iacute;cias, entre outros e juntos j&aacute; somam 10 milh&otilde;es de downloads. Possui a mais completa plataforma de produtos e servi&ccedil;os da internet nas &aacute;reas de publicidade, mobile, meios de pagamento online e presencial (PagSeguro), solu&ccedil;&otilde;es de hospedagem para pequenas e m&eacute;dias empresas (UOL HOST), solu&ccedil;&otilde;es completas em Outsourcing de TI para grandes empresas (UOLDIVEO), plataforma completa de Cloud Computing (UOL CLOUD), cursos online (UOL Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o), seguran&ccedil;a (Antiv&iacute;rus e Assist&ecirc;ncia T&eacute;cnica), produtos de Mobilidade (Wi-Fi) e Entretenimento (Games e Clube UOL), entre outros.&nbsp;</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (285, N'089d50b2-9fdf-4b17-84ef-1787e783c34e', 144, 1, N'<p>Initially focused on the production of documentaries and music videos, over the years TvZERO has incorporated several production segments, and now focuses exclusively on the production of content for cinema, TV and new media, always aiming the variety of content and technical excellence. TvZERO&#39;s most recent works are the feature films "Nise - The Heart of Madness" (Roberto Berliner), a fiction released in 2016 and winner of more than 20 international prizes such as Best Film at Tokyo International Film Festival and "Confessions of a Brazilian Call Girl" that took more than 2 millions viewers to Brazilian theaters. On TV, the production company released the series "Adoption Chronicles", broadcasted on GNT Channel, and #callmebruna on Fox Premium, already on its second season. Also in 2017, TvZERO released the film "Gabriel and the Mountain" (Fellipe Barbosa), winner of two awards at the Critics&#39; Week at Cannes Film Festival. At the beginning of 2018, TvZERO will release "492" (Henrique Goldman) and the co-productions "Loveling" (Gustavo Pizzi) and "La Familia Submergida" (Mar&iacute;a Alche).</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (286, N'f43ba369-8063-4163-9936-8f8ef1906ee8', 144, 2, N'<p>Produtora inicialmente focada na produ&ccedil;&atilde;o de document&aacute;rios e v&iacute;deos musicais, a TvZERO incorporou v&aacute;rios segmentos e agora se concentra exclusivamente na produ&ccedil;&atilde;o de conte&uacute;do cinematogr&aacute;fico, TV e novas m&iacute;dias, prezando sempre pela variedade de conte&uacute;do e pelo alto valor de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o.  Os trabalhos mais destacados da TvZero foram o longa-metragem de fic&ccedil;&atilde;o "Nise - O Cora&ccedil;&atilde;o da Loucura" (Roberto Berliner), lan&ccedil;ado em 2016, levando 153 mil espectadores aos cinemas e mais de 20 pr&ecirc;mios em festivais internacionais como o de Melhor Filme no Festival Internacional de Cinema de T&oacute;quio, e o filme Bruna Surfistinha (Marcus Baldini) com mais de 2 milh&otilde;es de espectadores no Brasil. Na TV, foram as s&eacute;ries "Hist&oacute;rias de Ado&ccedil;&atilde;o” (Roberto Berliner e Pablo Francischelli), "Eu Sou Assim" (Duda Vaisman e Calvito Leal) e "Eu, Adolescente" (Roberto Berliner, Chris Alcazar e Vitor Leite) veiculadas no canal GNT e #mechamadebruna cuja segunda temporada est&aacute; no ar nesse ano de 2017 na Fox Premium. Tamb&eacute;m este ano, a produtora lan&ccedil;ou o filme "Gabriel e a Montanha" (Fellipe Barbosa), vencedor de dois pr&ecirc;mios na Semana da Cr&iacute;tica no Festival de Cannes e no inicio do ano que vem, lan&ccedil;ar&aacute; "O Nome da Morte" (Henrique Goldman) e as coprodu&ccedil;&otilde;es "Benzinho" (Gustavo Pizzi) e "A Familia Submersa" (Mar&iacute;a Alche).</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
