INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (291, N'c363b719-441b-4e4d-9d5c-fc46b83a3950', 147, 1, N'<p>With 15&nbsp;years of experience in creating and producing content, Urca Filmes is now a<br />
benchmark of efficiency and excellence in the Brazilian TV and Cinema markets. The<br />
company combines a creative production mentality with pragmatism, commitment to<br />
quality of delivery and an extensive network of talents and collaborators. Urca Filmes has<br />
a track record that draws attention to the relevance of its portfolio which aims to<br />
strengthen Brazil&#39;s identity through careful selection of themed productions.</p>

<p><br />
One of the cultural cornerstones of the production house is to headstart its projects by<br />
doing a careful feasibility study which culminates in a production design (for development<br />
and production) for each individual project. This design always aims to meet the<br />
expectations of customers, partners and the project&rsquo;s audience.</p>

<p><br />
Urca&rsquo;s mission is to enhance the financial and human capitals available for each project so<br />
that they can result in moving images and sounds that have the power to inspire,<br />
entertain, educate, excite and - why not? - improve people&#39;s lives.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (292, N'cfe23f72-6f5a-4fa5-8c28-e6b05b46cfe7', 147, 2, N'<p>Com 15 anos de experi&ecirc;ncia na cria&ccedil;&atilde;o e produ&ccedil;&atilde;o de conte&uacute;do, a Urca Filmes &eacute; uma refer&ecirc;ncia de efici&ecirc;ncia e excel&ecirc;ncia no mercado audiovisual brasileiro. A produtora combina uma mentalidade de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o criativa com pragmatismo,&nbsp;compromisso com a qualidade do delivery e uma extensa rede de talentos e colaboradores. A Urca Filmes tem um <em>track record&nbsp;</em>que chama a aten&ccedil;&atilde;o pela relev&acirc;ncia de seu <em>portfolio, </em>que tem por objetivo fortalecer a identidade cultural do Brazil atrav&eacute;s de uma criteriosa sele&ccedil;&atilde;o de suas produ&ccedil;&otilde;es.</p>

<p>Um dos pilares da cultura de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o da Urca Filmes&nbsp;&eacute; sempre iniciar cada projeto com um cuidadoso estudo de viabilidade de modo a propor um desento de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o (tanto para o desenvolvimento, quanto para a realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o) que leve em conta suas singularidades, assim como as expectativas dos seus&nbsp;&nbsp;clientes, parceiros e do seu p&uacute;blico alvo de cada projeto avaliado.</p>

<p>A miss&atilde;o da Urca Filmes &eacute; potencializar&nbsp;o capital financeiro e&nbsp;humano dispon&iacute;vel em cada projeto de modo que ele possa se transformar em imagens em movimento e som que t&ecirc;m o poder de inspirar, entreter, educar, excitar e - porque n&atilde;o - melhorar a vida das pessoas.</p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (293, N'076f3df7-821e-4cea-b736-1264de61a62e', 148, 1, N'<p>Vewd brings you all the leading entertainment from around the world, connecting consumers everywhere, to the content they love.</p>

