INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (299, N'dde6aedd-48d3-4d43-8a58-4e313d4449e3', 151, 1, N'<p>The first channel in Latin America focused on action sports and young behavior: Music, Lifestyle, Surfing, Series, Culture, Skate, News, Travel, Gastronomy, Health, Electronic Magazines, Events, Graffiti, MTB, talk shows and many more.</p>

<p>Woohoo was born with more than 5,000 hours of program stock accumulated throughout its trajectory. From the program &quot;Recapture&quot; (TV Record: 1983-1991) Vibration (TV Record: 1984-1991), Ombak (MTV: 1991 -1993), RIP / WQS / Impact Zone / The History of Brazilian Surfing / Globosat: X Dream Series &amp; Extreme Series (Production for more than 15 countries: 1999 - 2001), Documentary F&aacute;bio Fabuloso (Cinema: 2004).</p>

<p>On May 22, 2006, we started the Canal transmissions. Between 2007 and 2009, the channel began to be distributed throughout the country through the main Brazilian Pay-Per-View TV operators: Claro TV, Telef&ocirc;nica, Vivo digital, Oi TV, Sky and other operations.</p>

<p>In 2012, ANCINE - National Agency of Cinema and TV, grants to WOOHOO the credentials of Qualified Space Brazilian Channel.</p>

<p>In 2013, Woohoo is present in approximately 80% of the pay TV households in Brazil, as well as starting operations in Portugal, Angola, Cape Verde and Uruguay. ; the Channel is present in more than 14 million subscribers in all the operators.</p>

<p>In the year 2015, the channel takes another step by providing its HD-quality programming in VOD through NET&#39;s and Claro TV&#39;s subscriber base service.</p>

<p>In 2016 Woohoo completes 10 years of uninterrupted programming on the air.</p>

<p><em><strong>In November 2017 the Channel will be shown in HD at the base of NET and Claro TV.</strong></em></p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
GO
INSERT [dbo].[HoldingDescriptions] ([Id], [Uid], [HoldingId], [LanguageId], [Value], [IsDeleted], [CreateDate], [CreateUserId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId]) VALUES (300, N'4768562b-2339-4ee7-a75b-c18fd31494f2', 151, 2, N'<p>O primeiro Canal da Am&eacute;rica Latina voltado para esportes de a&ccedil;&atilde;o e comportamento jovem: M&uacute;sica, Estilo de vida, Surfe, S&eacute;ries, Cultura, Skate, Noticias, Viagem, Gastronomia, Sa&uacute;de, Revistas eletr&ocirc;nicas, Eventos, Grafite, MTB, talk Shows e muitos mais.</p>

<p>Woohoo nasceu com mais de 5.000 horas de estoque de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o acumulados durante toda a sua trajet&oacute;ria. Desde o programa Realce (TV Record: 1983-1991) Vibra&ccedil;&atilde;o ( TV Record: 1984-1991 ), Ombak (MTV: 1991&nbsp; -1993), RIP / WQS / Zona de Impacto / A Hist&oacute;ria do Surfe Brasileiro /(Globosat: 1994- - 2005), X Dream Series &amp; Extreme Series (Produ&ccedil;&atilde;o para mais de 15 pa&iacute;ses: 1999 &ndash; 2001), Document&aacute;rio F&aacute;bio Fabuloso (Cinema: 2004).</p>

<p>Em 22 de maio de 2006 tivemos o in&iacute;cio das transmiss&otilde;es do Canal. Entre 2007 a 2009 o Canal passou a ter distribui&ccedil;&atilde;o em todo territ&oacute;rio nacional atrav&eacute;s das principais operadoras de TV por Assinatura do Brasil: Claro TV, Telef&ocirc;nica, Vivo digital, Oi TV, posteriormente Sky e outras opera&ccedil;&otilde;es.</p>

<p>Em 2012, a ANCINE &ndash; Ag&ecirc;ncia Nacional de Cinema e TV, concede ao WOOHOO as credenciais de Canal Brasileiro de Espa&ccedil;o Qualificado.</p>

<p>J&aacute; em 2013 o Woohoo est&aacute; presente em aproximadamente 80% dos domic&iacute;lios de TV paga no Brasil al&eacute;m de iniciar suas opera&ccedil;&otilde;es em Portugal, Angola, Cabo Verde e Uruguai. ; o Canal est&aacute; presente em mais de 14 milh&otilde;es de assinantes em todas as operadoras.</p>

<p>No ano de 2015 o canal d&aacute; mais um passo ao disponibilizar sua programa&ccedil;&atilde;o, com qualidade HD, em VOD, atrav&eacute;s do servi&ccedil;o para base de assinantes da NET e da Claro TV.</p>

<p>Em 2016 o Woohoo completa 10 anos de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o ininterrupta no ar.</p>

<p><em><strong>Em novembro de 2017 o Canal passa ser exibido em HD na base das Operadoras NET e Claro TV.</strong></em></p>
', 0, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1, CAST(N'2019-08-09 13:30:17.423' AS DateTime), 1)
